        },
        {
            "title": "國際｜據報美國向伊朗提交15點旨在結束中東戰事計劃",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜據報美國向伊朗提交15點旨在結束中東戰事計劃\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜據報美國向伊朗提交15點旨在結束中東戰事計劃</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據以色列第12頻道(Israeli Channel 12)電視台周二報道，美國有意提出為期一個月的停火方案，以便與伊朗討論一份包含15個要點、旨在結束戰爭的協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報，雙方將在擬議的為期一個月停火期間，就包含15點內容的計劃進行談判，這15點計劃包括允許國際原子能機構(IAEA)全面獲取所有信息、將濃縮鈾移交給IAEA、停止支持代理武裝組織，以及重開霍爾木茲海峽等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《紐約時報》報道稱，美國透過巴基斯坦遞交這份15點計劃，巴基斯坦陸軍參謀長穆尼爾(Syed Asim Munir)已成為兩國之間的關鍵中間人，據悉，穆尼爾與伊朗伊斯蘭革命衞隊保持密切聯繫。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗方面只是證實透過調解人，收到來自美國就要求談判發來的信息，德黑蘭正在審視有關內容。伊朗同日公布，任命曾經擔任革命衞隊副司令的佐爾加德爾(Mohammad Bagher Zolghadr)，接任最高國家安全委員會秘書。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%90%91%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A415%E9%BB%9E%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E6%88%B0%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-023135210.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 10:40:13",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "澳洲2月CPI略為降溫 但潛在通脹壓力仍存",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XvSHREwNhx99qUIHsn593A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEDA2045_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 澳洲統計局週三公布的數據顯示,澳洲2月消費者通脹略有緩解,但潛在價格壓力仍然頑固,支持了央行將在政策上保持謹慎的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至2月的12個月內,消費者物價指數(CPI)上漲3.7%,低於1月的漲幅和市場預期的3.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按季度計算,第一季度CPI上漲0.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政策制定者密切關注的核心通脹指標顯示,價格壓力持續存在。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月修剪均值CPI年增3.3%,較前月的3.4%有所下降,而加權中位數指標則從3.6%小幅降至約3.5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-86391d9a-7606-3688-9e64-de915e9b6f30-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">住房仍是年度通脹的最大推動因素,全年上漲7.2%,主要受電價上漲、租金上漲和新住宅價格上漲推動。電價年增37%,反映出家庭用盡政府補貼的影響。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">食品和非酒精飲料價格較去年同期上漲3.1%,其中外賣餐點和紅肉價格錄得顯著增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相比之下,交通成本年減0.2%,因汽車燃料價格下跌7.2%,儘管近期地緣政治緊張局勢令前景蒙上陰影。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局價格統計主管Sue-Ellen Luke表示,2月年度通脹\"略有緩解\",而潛在通脹則保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些數據強化了市場預期,即政策制定者將在更長時間內維持較高利率,以尋求將通脹率恢復至目標水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
